<div type="definition">
<p>IMAGE SHOWING OR PROVING that a FUTURE EVENT will HAPPEN.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The current general term for a presage is zhào 兆.</p>
<p>2. Xiáng 祥 is a less momentous sign or portent, positive or negative.</p>
        </div>
